A man was found hanging from a tree in Bloemfontein  on Thursday morning. Police spokesperson Col Thandi Mbambo said the discovery was made just after 6.30am  at the corner of Charles and Aliwal Streets. The unknown man was wearing blue shorts and an orange golf T-shirt. Mbambo said his black jeans were  found on the ground. “No foul play is suspected at this stage and a case of inquest has been registered for further investigation.” TimesLIVE